						<li><a href="http://gomakethings.com/icon-fonts/">Icon fonts</a>, a lightweight, scalable way to include icons.</li>
						<li><a href="https://github.com/toddmotto/fluidvids">FluidVids.js</a>, a lightweight javascript snippet for fluid iframes.</li>
